{"tid":2065722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英外相藍韜文：滙豐銀行支持國安法，抵觸了英國政府的反對立場","createTime":"2020-06-15T19:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T02:31:43.000Z","uid":53844,"like":282,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff72997dbfc7e428d4cc04f3bece323d8bc4b6b","tid":2065722,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T19:07:38.000Z","msg":"藍韜文隱晦批評滙豐支持北京在港訂立港區國安法<br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文隱晦批評滙豐銀行支持北京，在香港訂立「港區國安法」，牴觸英國政府的反對立場。<br />\n<br />\n滙控亞太區行政總裁王冬勝，早前曾經到街站簽名支持訂立「港區國安法」，引來英國及美國多名政客批評。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文在記者會上，被問到英國政府有什麼回應時說，相信企業會作出自己的判斷，但重申英國政府不會為了銀行家的利益，而犧牲香港人。 <br />\n<br />\n藍韜文強調，英國在維護港人自治與保障自由方面，作出了歷史承諾，這個是原則，強調會堅定支持香港人，又<span style=\"color: red;\">認為中國仍然有機會不執行有爭議的「港區國安法」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-16 02:46:58<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532253-20200616.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532253-20200616.htm&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7qjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=d536eca7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532253-20200616.htm&h=b2c303cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532253-20200616.htm</a>"},{"pid":"86266a2cee05e077164248e027083ef0e501c85b","tid":2065722,"uid":7860,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T19:09:11.000Z","msg":"睇黎滙豐真係冇得番身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4e2bee4c5ae5915998fbaa8c3f191b4da684e2","tid":2065722,"uid":47356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86266a2cee05e077164248e027083ef0e501c85b","tid":2065722,"uid":7860,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T19:09:11.000Z","msg":"睇黎滙豐真係冇得番身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T19:10:04.000Z","msg":"死硬啦"},{"pid":"68e1c59669fa9101d90618231d617ed7ab237f1f","tid":2065722